room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by Quest Factor in Seattle
review: I went to the Bank heist at the Redmond quest factor place and had the best time celebrating my boyfriends birthday! It was really exciting to try to cooperate with each other with all these clues and tricks that the room had in store. I 100% recommend the Redmond quest factor and I would love to come again!

room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by Quest Factor in Seattle
review: A couple days ago, I was able to visit Quest Factor with my friends. We did Bank Heist: Mission Impossible and had so much fun! If you want to have a great and fun time with your friends, I can definitely advise you to go to Quest Factor. There is an amazing atmosphere, beautiful decorations and interesting puzzles.Thank you a lot, Quest Factor, for a good time, we are looking forward to try new upcoming quests!

room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by Quest Factor in Seattle
review: I took a group of 11 and 12 year old boys here for a Birthday Party! They did the Bank Heist! I was so impressed with everything there! This was our very first escape room and it was amazing, it looked like a real bank, and with the help of the very nice gentleman working there they solved it. Was super fun and now we want to go back. The facility was perfect for a party and very clean! Loved everything about it and the kids had a Blast!!!!
